data-triple-N3.o: "1986 was a common year that started on a Wednesday, in accordance with the Gregorian calendar. It is the 1986th year of the Common Era, or A.D. ; the 986th year of the 2nd millennium; the 86th year of the 20th century; and the 7th year of the 1980s. The year 1986 was designated as the International Year of Peace by the United Nations."@en
